Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@FOT-TsukuAntiqueLMin Std L\fr-90\blur3\fs75\b1\1c&H00FDFCFC\3c&H000000&\3aA0\pos(1514,540)}原來我是個除了魔法之外\N毫無價{\fn@方正FW筑紫古典L明朝 简\fr-90\blur3\fs61\b0\1c&H00FDFCFC\3c&H000000&\3aA0\pos(1514,540)}值{\fn@FOT-TsukuAntiqueLMin Std L\fr-90\blur3\fs75\b1\1c&H00FDFCFC\3c&H000000&\3aA0\pos(1514,540)}的女人……
